snippet.textDisplay:
Oh my. In Hollywood. We must remember this is the entertainment industry. May we learn to relax a little more and allow ourselves to understand their are real people struggling to live in this world as best as we can. Some of us are struggling with medical issues. Financial issues and with mental issues which we are asking help with. Yet we are being missed in these needs.
The State of Colorado is back logged by three months. This doesn't stop the little people here on the bottom in need of serious medical attention. I have recently been diagnosed with a possible case of lupus. Which explains the physical reasons why I try and work only having to resign from work because my pain is too much to bare at times. I cannot even pay for medical care. Lord knows I cannot afford another hospital bill over my head. This is another reason some people who are hurting cannot get completely fixed medically. If your poor in this 🌎. Your just butt out of luck, & that stinks.
Then people may formulate their own opinions as to why a man woman or child cannot improve their living conditions. Even though we want to deep inside. Yet because we cannot afford basic care, we suffer for it mentally, emotionally, physically and spiritually. This is why I and possibly others feel as we are an outcasts to the general public. When will the people who have been struggling to survive in poverty finally have our breakthroughs. I am one of them. Extremely poor. Im not ashamed to speak my truth. Even if others choose to snicker at me or others in this same living conditions. May Jesus help us have an opportunity to have our basic needs met. In Jesus name I pray.
